ğŸ”¹ Minikube is a lightweight Kubernetes tool that lets you spin up a single-node cluster locally. Perfect for developers and testers, it offers a sandbox environment to:
âœRun a Kubernetes cluster on your local machine (Windows/macOS/Linux)
